                           <br>
                           <br>
                           Some of these come from older Masters who rely on obscure texts that might not be relevant to today's times. They have lived in an era with different mentalities.
                           <br>
                           <br>
                           At best, these people are doing their best to warn you of their beliefs. At worst, they are using fear to lure you into their sales funnels. To buy more ornaments, rituals and even burial services.
                           <br>
                           <br>
                           We take a statistical approach, weighing claims against probability and using Bazi principles to reduce uncertainty.
                           <br>
                           <br>
                           We explain how we arrive at our conclusions, helping you learn enough to discern the market better so you don't get overcharged by one-off consultations that are hard to follow-up on after your next luck cycle.
                           <br>
                           <br>
                           Lastly, when was the last time you saw easy-to-use Bazi software that could do personalised readings not just for you, but for your entire network?
                           <br>
                           <br>
                           If we did, then we wouldn't make this in the first place.
                           </div>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

